ard.com/uharlan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Harlan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 264<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/18/02 4:29:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ssra: Any words of Advice</span><hr size=1> Rhag 1 can be done with 6-8 well-equipped 60's. However, if your top tank is only 55 I'd be wary.<br> <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=155719&resize=true">Harlan</a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueasirok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>easirok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 84<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/20/02 11:51:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ssra: Any words of Advice</span><hr size=1> Honestly, dont bother with Rhag 1 unless you are prepared to CR. Since this is your first time in ssra, you will have a hard time just clearing the regular mobs until you get the hang of it.<br><br>You really want a 60 warrior for tanking (their taunt capability is significantly better), and a 60 monk or SK for pulling/splitting.<br><br>You can always invis all the way to rhag 1's room... nothing usually sees through invis to there. However, if your tank is only lvl 55 I would bet the damage Rhag puts out will be above and beyond anything he is familiar with.<br><br>Course its always fun to bet against the odds and try it anyways <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I would doubt however that you will even see Rhag1 up... he is usually a farmed mob, killed as soon as he spawns.<br> <p><hr width=100%>Easirok Soulsavior<br>Crusader of Stormhammer<br>Subject of Vexare<br><a target="_blank" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=53778">Easirok's Magelo Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.showPrevMessage?topicID=166.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.showNextMessage?topicID=166.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=2><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=166.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.threadControl?topicID=166.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=166.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=166.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=p